            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Cut</strong> 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">(8)</span> pieces of tin foil approx. the size of an A3 sheet of paper</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lay</strong> each tofu steak in the middle of 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">(4)</span> pieces of foil (doubling the foil prevents any leakages!)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Spoon</strong> the marinade over the tofu and scrunch the edges of the foil together to form a sealed parcel, then place them on a baking tray and put then in the oven for 15 min&nbsp;</p>",
